          <div style="font-family:monospace; background:var(--lav1); border-radius:6px; padding:3px 8px; font-size:13px; color:var(--purple); display:inline-block; margin:4px 0;">/θæŋk juː/</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#666;">Put your tongue between your teeth! Not /f/ !</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; border:2px solid var(--yellow);">
          <div style="font-size:22px; margin-bottom:6px;">🔤 W sound</div>
          <div style="font-weight:800; color:var(--deep); font-size:15px;">"Water" / "Would"</div>
          <div style="font-family:monospace; background:var(--lav1); border-radius:6px; padding:3px 8px; font-size:13px; color:var(--purple); display:inline-block; margin:4px 0;">/ˈwɔː.tər/ /wʊd/</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#666;">Round lips like a kiss, then open! Not /v/ !</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; border:2px solid var(--yellow);">
          <div style="font-size:22px; margin-bottom:6px;">🔤 H sound</div>
          <div style="font-weight:800; color:var(--deep); font-size:15px;">"Hot chocolate"</div>
          <div style="font-family:monospace; background:var(--lav1); border-radius:6px; padding:3px 8px; font-size:13px; color:var(--purple); display:inline-block; margin:4px 0;">/hɒt ˈtʃɒk.lət/</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#666;">A soft breath of air — like fogging a mirror!</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; border:2px solid var(--yellow);">
          <div style="font-size:22px; margin-bottom:6px;">🔤 CH sound</div>
